---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <Header
    imagePath="/src/assets/pin.png"
    menuPath="/src/assets/burger.png"
    altText="location"
  />
  <section class="bg-gray-100 py-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <div class="p-6">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">About Us</h1>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We are a team of passionate individuals dedicated to delivering
            innovative solutions and exceptional experiences. Our mission is to
            provide high-quality products and services that meet the needs of
            our clients and exceed their expectations.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            With years of experience in the industry, we have developed a deep
            understanding of the challenges and opportunities faced by
            businesses today. We leverage our expertise to deliver tailored
            solutions that drive growth and success.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <div class="p-6 flex items-center">
          <div class="mr-6">
            <img
              src="/src/assets/dhia.png"
              alt="DHia' SHalabi"
              class="w-full h-64 object-contain rounded-lg border-4 border-gray-200 shadow-lg"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="w-2/3">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">
              Meet Our Founder
            </h2>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
              DHia' SHalabi
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">CEO & Founder</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              As the CEO and Founder of our company, DHia' SHalabi brings a
              wealth of experience and a visionary approach to leadership. With
              a deep commitment to innovation and excellence, DHia' has been the
              driving force behind our success and growth. Under their guidance,
              our team continues to thrive and achieve new heights.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <li>
              <strong>Innovation:</strong> We constantly seek new and creative ways
              to solve problems and deliver value.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Integrity:</strong> We conduct our business with honesty and
              transparency.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Customer Focus:</strong> We prioritize the needs and satisfaction
              of our clients above all else.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Excellence:</strong> We strive for excellence in everything
              we do.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Milestones</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">2024</h3>
              <p>
                Launched our new product line and expanded to international
                markets.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">2023</h3>
              <p>Received the industry award for best customer service.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">2022</h3>
              <p>Reached 100,000 satisfied customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Join Us in Our Journey</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We are always looking for talented individuals to join our team. If
          you share our passion for excellence and innovation, weâ€™d love to hear
          from you.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="bg-white text-blue-600 py-2 px-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
          >Explore Careers</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
